tr.td: DescriptionImperfect competition in the short run.svg

td.div: English: Short-run equilibrium of a monopoly, oligopoly, or a firm under monopolistic competition. The grey box illustrates abnormal profit, though the firm could just as easily be making a loss. The same diagram could equally represent the longrun equilibria of monopoly and oligopoly.
